{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was a student in the '60s, a time of social upheaval and questioning,"},{"time":5306,"text":"and -- on a personal level -- an awakening sense of idealism."},{"time":9932,"text":"The war in Vietnam was raging, the Civil Rights movement was under way"},{"time":14137,"text":"and pictures had a powerful influence on me."},{"time":17283,"text":"Our political and military leaders were telling us one thing"},{"time":20906,"text":"and photographers were telling us another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23619,"text":"I believed the photographers and so did millions of other Americans."},{"time":28163,"text":"Their images fuelled resistance to the war and to racism."},{"time":32324,"text":"They not only recorded history -- they helped change the course of history."},{"time":36968,"text":"Their pictures became part of our collective consciousness"},{"time":40586,"text":"and, as consciousness evolved into a shared sense of conscience,"},{"time":44479,"text":"change became not only possible, but inevitable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47767,"text":"It puts a human face on issues which, from afar,"},{"time":51518,"text":"can appear abstract or ideological or monumental in their global impact."},{"time":56925,"text":"What happens at ground level, far from the halls of power,"},{"time":61570,"text":"happens to ordinary citizens one by one."},{"time":64992,"text":"And I understood that documentary photography"},{"time":67315,"text":"has the ability to interpret events from their point of view."},{"time":71805,"text":"It gives a voice to those who otherwise would not have a voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75853,"text":"My TED wish. Thereâ€™s a vital story that needs to be told"},{"time":81338,"text":"and I wish for TED to help me gain access to it"},{"time":84945,"text":"and then to help me come up with innovative and exciting ways"},{"time":88529,"text":"to use news photography in the digital era."},{"time":91778,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98164,"text":"[ 10.3.08 -- The story breaks. ]"},{"time":104948,"text":"[ \"I have been a witness, and these pictures are my testimony.\" ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110876,"text":"[ South Africa ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128919,"text":"[ This is happening now. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132048,"text":"[ Cambodia ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":147438,"text":"[ Swaziland ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160466,"text":"[ One person dies every 20 seconds. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164482,"text":"[ Thailand ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177606,"text":"[ An ancient disease is taking on a deadly new form. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182004,"text":"[ Siberia ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":193676,"text":"[ Lesotho ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":206436,"text":"[ Tuberculosis: the next pandemic? ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210445,"text":"[ India ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223185,"text":"[ TB is preventable and curable, ]"},{"time":230784,"text":"[ but it is mutating due to inadequate treatment. ]"},{"time":239969,"text":"[ XDR-TB: ]"},{"time":242223,"text":"[ extreme drug resistant tuberculosis. ]"},{"time":246699,"text":"[ There is no reliable cure. ]"},{"time":254647,"text":"[ Patients often die within weeks of diagnosis. ]"},{"time":261918,"text":"[ 49 countries have reported XDR-TB. ]"},{"time":269484,"text":"[ XDR-TB is a critical threat to global health. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277438,"text":"[ Extreme outbreak, suffering, affliction ]"},{"time":278688,"text":"[ Extreme loss, pain, pandemic ]"},{"time":286401,"text":"[ Extremely preventable. ]"},{"time":289504,"text":"[ XDR-TB. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":295742,"text":"[ We can stop this now. ]"},{"time":303273,"text":"[ Spread the story. Stop the disease. ]"},{"time":308734,"text":"[ Go to XDRTB.org now. ]"},{"time":312347,"text":"[ XDRTB.org: we are the treatment. ]"},{"time":316930,"text":"[ We are the treatment. ]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321371,"text":"[ Made possible through the kind support of BD. ]"}]}]}